A bus and minibus taxi collided in Leeu Gamka. Authorities allege a tyre on the taxi burst sending it head-on into the bus. The bus was travelling from Beaufort West to Cape Town when the crash happened. #DStv403 CAPE TOWN - At least 11 people have been killed in a major accident on the N-1 highway in the Western Cape. A bus and minibus taxi collided in Leeu Gamka. Authorities allege a tyre on the taxi burst sending it head-on into the bus. The bus was travelling from Beaufort West to Cape Town when the crash happened.